title: AHS: Hotel (2015) - "End Credits Score"
author: American Horror Story: Croatia
comment: This reminds me when it was holidays I would watch Hotel episode after episode while eating Hoola Hoops
The scores for this show are amazing!!!! 😭😭😭
I can just picture myself walking down the catwalk in 24 inch heels as blood rains down while I'm striking poses along with this track
The best end credits song of all seasons!!
this was used in the actual episodes if I remember correctly
